Install VS studio with c++ desktop pack and mark MSVCxxx and some windows SDK to the install https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeBzSYiWkEU 
install VS code and download the extensions "CMake Tools(Microsoft)" and "C/C++(Microsoft)" 

To make this project work, install VCPKG, which will also install Cmake https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/vcpkg/get_started/get-started-msbuild?pivots=shell-cmd 

Add "C:\path\to\vcpkg" to PATH in environment variables

Different compilers can be installed via https://youtu.be/8jLOx1hD3_o?t=667 

VCPKG does not work easy with GCC compiler
